1
00:00:48,460 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 13=

3
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:57,520
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

4
00:00:57,679 --> 00:00:59,640
Consort Li is carrying the royal child.

5
00:01:00,079 --> 00:01:00,719
Really?

6
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,120
Liuli,

7
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,879
we're going to have a child.

8
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:11,840
By my decree.

9
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:16,120
Consort Li is virtuous and gentle,

10
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:17,599
and well-versed in propriety.

11
00:01:18,079 --> 00:01:20,359
She is hereby elevated
to the rank of Noble Consort Li.

12
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,480
She shall oversee
all affairs of the inner court.

13
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:24,640
Congratulations, Noble Consort!

14
00:01:24,799 --> 00:01:27,239
May you be blessed
with boundless fortune, Noble Consort!

15
00:01:29,079 --> 00:01:30,719
I wonder
if it will be a princess or a prince.

16
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:35,239
Which one does Your Majesty prefer?

17
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:37,439
I will love our child,

18
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:38,719
no matter what.

19
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:41,959
They will have the best thing
in the world.

20
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:45,400
Has Your Majesty chosen a name for them?

21
00:01:46,439 --> 00:01:47,920
I'll have to give it some thought.

22
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:51,280
I'll have all the officials
contribute their ideas.

23
00:01:51,719 --> 00:01:52,280
Wait.

24
00:01:53,079 --> 00:01:54,359
You should be the one to name the child.

25
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:55,200
Do you agree?

26
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:56,359
Yes, I do.

27
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,959
I've always hoped

28
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,879
to have a son and a daughter.

29
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:04,560
Tianzhen for one,

30
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,400
Wuxie for the other.

31
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:09,759
Or maybe Jixiang for one,

32
00:02:10,159 --> 00:02:11,240
Ruyi for the other.

33
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:13,960
They all sound beautiful.

34
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:15,400
Whatever you say.

35
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,439
Yes.

36
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:43,719
Your Majesty.

37
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:44,919
Your Majesty.

38
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,520
Your Majesty.

39
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,879
What a perfect opportunity.

40
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:58,220
(Slave)

41
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,639
(I hope that one day,)

42
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:14,159
(this hatred)

43
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:16,199
(can end with me.)

44
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:17,919
(Mu Ruyi.)

45
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:20,280
(Your Majesty.)

46
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:24,159
(Do you know)

47
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:26,560
(that your mercy
will be what ruins you?)

48
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:27,439
(Mother,)

49
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:29,000
(I've done as you commanded.)

50
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,719
(I've dealt with the Dongqing prisoners)

51
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:33,120
(by branding them
with the mark of slavery.)

52
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:34,800
(Don't you remember my words?)

53
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:38,080
(Dongqing and Xiling are sworn enemies.)

54
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:39,879
(Show them mercy,)

55
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,360
(and you are being cruel to yourself.)

56
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,560
(Guards.)

57
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,719
(Bury that Dongqing prisoner alive.)

58
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:45,240
(Yes.)

59
00:03:45,479 --> 00:03:46,000
(Wait!)

60
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:48,280
(Mother.)

61
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:50,919
(Though we've been at war
with Dongqing for generations,)

62
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,479
(those prisoners)

63
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,360
(are all of royal blood.)

64
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:56,840
(Some are even children of my age.)

65
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,800
(Mother, please spare their lives.)

66
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,479
(Do not sow more hatred with Dongqing.)

67
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,000
(They may seem like)

68
00:04:03,199 --> 00:04:05,360
(innocent, carefree youths now,)

69
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:07,039
(but mark my words,)

70
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:09,520
(they will grow
into our mortal enemies.)

71
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,840
(If we don't kill them,)

72
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:13,159
(it will leave a lasting danger.)

73
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,199
(Mother,)

74
00:04:14,479 --> 00:04:15,960
(I will be ruthless with them,)

75
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:19,600
(I'll ensure they never escape
the bonds of slavery.)

76
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,600
(But on one condition,)

77
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:24,240
(I beg you, Mother, spare their lives.)

78
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,680
(The one who plotted against me
so carefully,)

79
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:29,279
(the demon bent on destroying Xiling,)

80
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:32,199
(turns out to be
the very one I once saved.)

81
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,279
(How ironic.)

82
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:37,959
(This has to end now.)

83
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:43,360
Noble Consort,
do you have any instructions?

84
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:47,319
His Majesty is staying with me tonight.

85
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,839
You may rest now.

86
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:49,920
No need to keep watch.

87
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:51,160
Yes, My Lady.

88
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,000
Your Majesty.

89
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:19,120
Your Majesty.

90
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,680
Your Highness.

91
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,639
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

92
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:45,519
Mother!

93
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,519
Mother!

94
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:50,879
Mother!

95
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:52,680
Mother!

96
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:56,959
Ruyi,

97
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,519
it's you!

98
00:05:58,839 --> 00:06:00,480
- Mother, I've come to save you.
- My daughter!

99
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:02,560
You will suffer no more.

100
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:04,800
Let's go.

101
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,439
Your Majesty, Your Highness,

102
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,480
I know a secret way out of the city.

103
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:14,120
Follow me.

104
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:14,800
Go!

105
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,680
Get up, quickly.

106
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:23,319
Get up.

107
00:06:23,519 --> 00:06:24,000
Come on.

108
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,120
Let's go.

109
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,360
Your Majesty.

110
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:38,759
Are you alright?

111
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:40,199
Mo Shuo?

112
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:43,680
This is a unique knockout incense
from Xiling.

113
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,480
Where is Jing Liuli?

114
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:54,879
I had actually thought

115
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,399
that your warning was unnecessary,

116
00:06:58,199 --> 00:07:00,439
and I was foolish enough
to hope she wanted to start over.

117
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:02,120
Just as I thought,

118
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,800
we've come

119
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,240
to this point after all.

120
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:16,519
All guards, hear my command!

121
00:07:16,759 --> 00:07:17,319
Yes!

122
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:19,959
Capture the Xiling traitor,

123
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,279
Mu Ruyi!

124
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,319
Yes!

125
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:25,959
Your Highness, take a rest.

126
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,920
Let me help Her Majesty.

127
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,000
We must keep moving.

128
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,800
They could catch up at any moment.

129
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,600
Your Highness,
how is it that your health has declined?

130
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:38,279
Is an old wound acting up?

131
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,519
I'm with child.

132
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,120
My movements are much more limited now.

133
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,480
Watch out!

134
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:54,240
It's been so long.

135
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,759
Mu Ruyi.

136
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,319
Mo Shuo?

137
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,160
Why are you here?

138
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,240
Capture the Xiling remnants alive!

139
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:32,960
Mother!

140
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:37,480
Mother!

141
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:39,759
Mother!

142
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,200
Mother!

143
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,559
Your Highness!

144
00:08:57,279 --> 00:08:58,000
Ruyi.

145
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:00,879
Ruyi.

146
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:06,799
You're always my pride.

147
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:12,480
You must... must...

148
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,399
No!

149
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:23,120
You must survive.

150
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,240
Take back...

151
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:30,399
Take back...

152
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,080
Mother!

153
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,960
Mother!

154
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,399
Mother!

155
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,440
Mo Shuo,

156
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:55,080
I never knew you were with Ling Xiao!

157
00:09:56,639 --> 00:09:57,519
I'm such a fool.

158
00:09:58,759 --> 00:10:00,159
After all the trust I placed in you,

159
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:01,679
in the end,

160
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,720
it was all turned against me.

161
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,480
I'll kill you!

162
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,240
You want me dead, don't you?

163
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,960
Then we all die!

164
00:11:04,399 --> 00:11:05,759
Should I call you Mu Ruyi

165
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,600
or Jing Liuli?

166
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,399
I must admit,
your painstaking performance

167
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:13,120
has earned my admiration.

168
00:11:14,159 --> 00:11:14,879
And you?

169
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,320
Ling Xiao,

170
00:11:16,799 --> 00:11:18,080
with your false affection,

171
00:11:18,679 --> 00:11:20,840
you committed murder
in the name of love.

172
00:11:21,039 --> 00:11:23,039
Whether it was Mu Ruyi or Jing Liuli,

173
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,080
didn't you make promises
to both of them?

174
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:27,240
My performance

175
00:11:27,559 --> 00:11:30,159
can't match
even a fraction of your cruelty.

176
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,639
What exactly are you trying to do?

177
00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:34,320
I haven't yet killed you,

178
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,879
you lying wretch,

179
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:36,679
to avenge my mother

180
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:38,519
and my kingdom!

181
00:11:39,679 --> 00:11:41,039
Is your false affection

182
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:43,320
the way you seek revenge?

183
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:45,879
My false affection?

184
00:11:46,559 --> 00:11:48,039
And what about you?

185
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,559
You loved Jing Liuli

186
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,039
only for her obedience,

187
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,720
and you pity her background.

188
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,879
You never truly loved her.

189
00:11:56,879 --> 00:11:59,480
If you had even a shred of true feeling,

190
00:11:59,919 --> 00:12:02,000
you must be ready to lose everything.

191
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:06,279
Mu Ruyi,

192
00:12:07,399 --> 00:12:08,759
you're carrying our baby.

193
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:10,480
I hate you, Ling Xiao,

194
00:12:10,919 --> 00:12:12,240
including this baby.

195
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,519
Jing Liuli!

196
00:12:13,799 --> 00:12:15,120
I hate all these names.

197
00:12:15,279 --> 00:12:16,840
I hate him, and I hate you even more.

198
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:19,200
You are the one

199
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:20,639
who made me a monster.

200
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,879
We will burn to ash,

201
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:26,080
and never, ever meet again!
